<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="honour-n">hono(u)r <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'ɒnə(r)/    美 /'ɑːnər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] [常用单数] [正式用语] 荣幸；[U] 荣誉；[C] 荣誉称号：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I feel it a <strong>great honour</strong> to be invited.
承蒙邀请，深感荣幸。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is my / an honor to</strong> be here to share with you my opinions on what to learn in senior high school.
能在这里和大家分享在高中应该学什么的看法，我感到非常荣幸。</p><footer>2014 江西书面表达改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>achieve / attain / gain honour
获得荣誉</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The athletes competed for the <strong>honour of</strong> their countries.
运动员为自己国家的荣誉而比赛。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was chosen for the national honour of Teacher of the Year.
她荣获全国“年度最佳教师”称号。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 尊敬；敬意</strong></h4>
<p>great respect and admiration for sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>hold sb in honour
尊敬某人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We had a great party to show honour to the famous scientist.
我们举办了一个盛大的晚会以表示对这位著名科学家的敬意。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>正义感；道义</strong></h4>
<p>the quality of knowing and doing what is morally right：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a man of honour</strong>
品德高尚的人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a matter / point / question of honour</strong>
道义上的事</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>[与不定冠词连用] 光荣的人 / 事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She’s an honour to her family and her country.
她是家人和国家的光荣。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="have-the-honour-of-doing-sth">have the honour of (doing) sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>有幸做某事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>May I have the honour of this dance?
可以赏光和我跳这支舞吗？</p></div>

<h3 id="in-honour-of-sb-in-sbs-honour">in honour of sb / in sb's honour</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为向某人表示敬意；为纪念某人：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We celebrate Mother's Day in honour of our mothers.
我们庆祝母亲节是为了向母亲表示敬意。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A ceremony was held in those soldiers' honour.
人们举行了一个仪式来纪念那些战士。</p></div></div>